Title: A Visibility Representation for Graphs in Three Dimensions  
Author: Prosenjit Bose Hazel Everett Sandor P. Fekete Michael E. Houle Anna Lubiw Henk Meijer Kathleen Romanik Gunter Rote Thomas C. Shermer Sue Whitesides Christian Zelle 
